# UI build. `web/dist/.gitkeep` is committed so `//go:embed all:dist` in
# web/web.go succeeds on a fresh clone; the real bundle is regenerated by
# `bun run build` (Handler() returns nil — "UI disabled" — until then).
/web/node_modules/
/web/dist/*
!/web/dist/.gitkeep
/web/.vite/

